query:
INSERT INTO review_automation_logs (id, task_id, workspace_id, action, output, error_message)
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
            RETURNING
                id as "id!: Uuid",
                task_id as "task_id!: Uuid",
                workspace_id as "workspace_id!: Uuid",
                action as "action!: ReviewAction",
                output,
                error_message,
                created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
